skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nomad
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Nomad creates minimalist, practical tools that keep us powered on the go. We develop all of our product concepts including cell phone cases, iPhone straps and chargers from the ground up relying on the lightest, thinnest and strongest materials for our designs. 

You can use this skill to search for your favorite products and hear about our policies.
Here's how you can open this skill
"Alexa, open nomad".
Once inside the skill you can ask
- find me a case
- Search for wallets
- What's your return policy
